238
00:21:57,903 --> 00:21:59,071
Apa ini?

239
00:21:59,196 --> 00:22:01,823
"Putri sulung Wakil Pejabat Pengadilan
Park Jae-hak

240
00:22:01,907 --> 00:22:03,950
