00:22:12,376 --> 00:22:14,878
Dia Song Sa-hui yang kita kenal?

246
00:22:21,468 --> 00:22:22,552
Song Sa-hui itu?

247
00:22:25,764 --> 00:22:26,890
Ada apa, Pak?

248
00:22:27,516 --> 00:22:30,936
