381
00:37:22,590 --> 00:37:23,758
Dia takkan begitu.

382
00:37:24,342 --> 00:37:27,345
- Sudah kukatakan padamu.
- Aku serius.

383
00:37:27,637 --> 00:37:31,265
Wanita Istana Kim beri tahu Kasim Park,
