384
00:37:31,349 --> 00:37:33,225
dan aku tak sengaja mendengar mereka.

385
00:37:34,226 --> 00:37:35,227
Hei, Juru Tulis Song.

386
00:37:35,311 --> 00:37:37,772
Tidak, Magang Song,
kau harus beri tahu faktanya.

387
00:37:38,356 --> 00:37:40,775
Dia terus menyebarkan rumor aneh.

388
00:37:40,983 --> 00:37:42,026
Rumor apa?

389
00:37:42,109 --> 00:37:44,779
Bagaimana bisa kukatakan, ya?

390
00:37:44,862 --> 00:37:47,990
Hanya saja, kau tahu,

391
00:37:48,991 --> 00:37:51,869
