392
00:37:51,953 --> 00:37:54,246
Ayolah, tak masuk akal.

393
00:37:54,330 --> 00:37:57,792
Magang Song datang
bersama kami pagi ini...

394
00:37:58,876 --> 00:38:01,212
Dia tak datang bersama kita tadi.

395
00:38:07,927 --> 00:38:10,012
Juru Tulis Song, kenapa tak bicara?

396
00:38:10,096 --> 00:38:11,764
Katakan itu tak benar.

397
00:38:13,516 --> 00:38:14,600
Magang Song?

398
00:38:23,442 --> 00:38:24,610
Itu benar

399
00:38:26,028 --> 00:38:27,697
aku berada di Dongungjeon.

400
00:38:37,498 --> 00:38:38,499
Tunggu.

401
00:38:39,333 --> 00:38:40,376
Apa maksudmu?

402
00:38:41,627 --> 00:38:43,671
Tunggu, kau... Kau dan Yang Mulia...

