00:39:47,610 --> 00:39:51,447
Yang Mulia, Magang Song Sa-hui telah tiba.

420
00:39:58,329 --> 00:40:01,040
Kenapa kau kemari? Sebaiknya kau kembali.

421
00:40:02,374 --> 00:40:04,543
Dia petugas di Kantor Titah Kerajaan.

422
00:40:05,669 --> 00:40:08,923
Yang Mulia tak boleh menemuinya
tanpa sejarawan.

423
00:40:09,006 --> 00:40:10,216
Persilakan dia masuk.

424
00:40:35,741 --> 00:40:37,118
Aku mau kalian tetap di luar.

425
00:41:03,978 --> 00:41:05,146
Berani sekali kau.

