439
00:41:53,235 --> 00:41:54,445
Jangan salah paham.

440
00:41:55,237 --> 00:41:56,739
Walau kau berusaha keras,

441
00:41:57,531 --> 00:41:59,200
Pangeran takkan jadi milikmu.

